♪ What kind of town is it? ♪

286
00:36:59,234 --> 00:37:03,109
♪ Go switch the light on ♪
♪ so we can see... ♪

287
00:37:03,859 --> 00:37:05,151
♪ what's there... ♪

288
00:37:05,568 --> 00:37:09,943
♪ Switch it on and stop ♪
♪ your talking, too... ♪

289
00:37:10,043 --> 00:37:12,679
Sorry Sir!
This is the wrong girl.

290
00:37:12,829 --> 00:37:13,929
Huh?

291
00:37:14,318 --> 00:37:16,026
♪ so we can see ♪

292
00:37:16,256 --> 00:37:18,259
I thought she was a...

293
00:37:18,359 --> 00:37:21,734
♪ what a sight it is ♪
♪ Berlin by light ♪

294
00:37:22,776 --> 00:37:28,151
♪ Go switch the light on so ♪
